window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What would you do to get back home? </b></p> <p>Max and Mandy are stranded miles from camp. Their vehicle has been burned, along with most of their gear. The road ahead means danger and the unknown.&nbsp;</p> <p>Dan and Olivia are holed up in a suburban home. She's gravely injured, and Dan waits anxiously for the soldiers to return. Will he alone be able to defend the house?&nbsp;</p> <p>Georgia and the rest realize that Max and Mandy might not be returning. After the last attack, they know they have to step up their defenses. But will their efforts be enough to keep them alive?&nbsp;</p> <p><i>Getting Home</i>&nbsp;is book 7 of The EMP, a post-apocalyptic survival thriller series. It deals with real people fighting for their survival every inch of the way.</p>"; 
